testimonials.text: Chetan Oli is a quick learner with an excillent logical and programming skills. He picks up things or technology very quickly. I have worked with him for a year and it was really a good experience.
testimonials.user: Saurabh Thakur, System Engineer at Iris Software Inc.

testimonials.text: Chetan is one of the hardest working professionals that I have ever seen. He has a learning attitude towards everything, coding, sports(swimming, ice skating, carrom are the sports which I saw him playing) or anything with full interest and with a smile. We both worked together projects including Spring MVC Framework, responsiveness of websites and crypto currency websites in which he played important role in project. He is a guy with positive mindset, loyal, enthusiastic and is really helpful towards other people. I had a great time working with Chetan and I hope we will work again soon.
testimonials.user: Ashish Garg, Full Stack Developer at Newgen Software.

testimonials.text: It was fantastic to work together with Chetan, who is an exceptional Software Engineer. He has good command in Java (Spring Framework), .netCore, React.js and multiple Database technologies (MySql, PostgresSQL to name a few). Loyal, insightful and independent, he is always capable of adapting to new working environments and learning new technologies. He has very positive attitude towards work. He always meets the deadlines. I wish him best of all lucks for his future endeavours and strongly recommend him for his field.
